    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors have been reviewed against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain flagged as epistemic gaps. Despite achieved levels falling below required levels across all assessed factors, the assessment package is accepted as a complete and documented credibility evidence record for regulatory submission purposes, with the understanding that outstanding gaps must be resolved in a subsequent assessment cycle prior to marketing authorization. Monte Carlo UQ provides partial uncertainty coverage. The package is structurally complete under ProfileMinimal.",
